{"tid":738354,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"石原里美新劇《高嶺之花》","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T10:07:30.000Z","uid":77721,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5dc0be4b6e4723afd99206e04e3b21019903c6","tid":738354,"uid":77721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/204409_c6fd2103d1eb851109def62ec031f848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F204409_c6fd2103d1eb851109def62ec031f848.jpg&h=8e495720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《高嶺之花》<br />\n主演:石原里美、峯田和伸<br />\n<br />\n劇情簡介:<br />\n「高嶺之花」故事講述出生自名門「月島流」本家的月島桃，是一個擁攬美貌、事業、財力、顯赫家世及壓倒性才能的名媛。然而，原來計劃和心愛男子結婚，永浴愛河的她，卻發現對方劈腿，隨後就在結婚儀式當天解除婚約。面對這個本該不會發生在她的身上的事情，桃頓時喪失自信，自我崩壞&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n失去一切的桃，這時遇上無論外貌、事業、財力及家世，都一概沒有的平凡自行車店主・風間直人。「高嶺之花」遇上「一介凡夫」，條件懸殊的兩人，最後竟然墜入情網。究竟他們是否可以無視身邊的反對聲，並戰勝彼此間的障礙呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/204653_c270e107bcdb02e83b895674ebcab994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F204653_c270e107bcdb02e83b895674ebcab994.jpg&h=ef8d6744&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1b28ba4d639c9e567c59b9f7aafbbe672526c86","tid":738354,"uid":77721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"發現石原每次開新劇都無人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95def8e5f1139d74b099caa1c30ae50d5317a733","tid":738354,"uid":77721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"今晚香港時間9點播第一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02edd130d79ff38207d73e7a1a39ae26dcb0023a","tid":738354,"uid":178909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"里美bb世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji